## ğŸ“ Key Learnings

### 1. **Cloud vs Local Development**
- Ollama works great locally but can't be deployed
- Cloud APIs (Gemini) work everywhere but need internet

### 2. **API Model Selection**
- Not all model names work (404 errors)
- Pro models have strict quotas (use Flash models!)
- Always check rate limits for free tiers

### 3. **UI/UX Design**
- White text on white = invisible (color contrast matters!)
- Direct CSS injection more reliable than external files
- User feedback drives better design

### 4. **Deployment Challenges**
- Secrets MUST be in [.streamlit/secrets.toml](file:///c:/Users/vinay/Desktop/Ai-Powered-Legal-Chat-Bot/.streamlit/secrets.toml)
- Voice/microphone features don't work on cloud servers
- Disable gracefully with helpful messages

### 5. **Git & GitHub**
- Use [.gitignore](file:///c:/Users/vinay/Desktop/Ai-Powered-Legal-Chat-Bot/.gitignore) to protect secrets
- Never commit API keys to public repos
- Small, frequent commits are better

